\c 11
\s Ubukhulu beN\nd kosi\nd*
\p
\v 1 Ngakho wothanda iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho\x + 6.5.\x*, ugcine umlayo wayo lezimiso zayo lezahlulelo zayo lemithetho yayo insuku zonke\x + Levi 8.35. Hez. 44.16.\x*.
\v 2 Yazini lamuhla, ngoba kangikhulumi ebantwaneni benu abangakwaziyo labangakubonanga ukulaya kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu\x + 8.5.\x*, ubukhulu bayo\x + 3.24. 5.24.\x*, isandla sayo esilamandla, lengalo yayo eyeluliweyo\x + 4.34.\x*,
\v 3 lezibonakaliso zayo lezenzo zayo eyazenza phakathi kweGibhithe kuFaro inkosi yeGibhithe, lelizweni lakhe lonke\x + 6.22.\x*,
\v 4 lalokho eyakwenza ebuthweni leGibhithe, emabhizeni ayo lenqoleni zayo, lokuthi yenza amanzi oLwandle oluBomvu abakhukhule lapho bexotshana lani, lokuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* yababhubhisa, kuze kube lamuhla\x + Eks. 14.27,28. 15.9,10.\x*,
\v 5 lalokho eyakwenza kini enkangala laze lafika kulindawo,
\v 6 lalokho eyakwenza kuDathani lakuAbiramu amadodana kaEliyabi indodana kaRubeni, ukuthi umhlaba wakhamisa umlomo wawo wabaginya bona labezindlu zabo, lamathente abo\x + Nani 16.1,31. 27.3. Hlab. 106.17.\x*, lakho konke okwakungokwabo, phakathi kukaIsrayeli wonke\x + Gen. 7.4,23.\x*.
\v 7 Kodwa amehlo enu abonile zonke izenzo ezinkulu zeN\nd kosi\nd* eyazenzayo.
\v 8 Ngakho lizagcina yonke imithetho engikulaya yona lamuhla, ukuze libe lamandla lingene lidle ilifa lelizwe, elichaphela kulo ukuyakudla ilifa lalo\x + Josh. 1.6,7.\x*,
\v 9 lokuthi lelule izinsuku elizweni\x + 4.40.\x* iN\nd kosi\nd* eyalifungela oyihlo ukubanika lona lenzalo yabo\x + Gen. 50.24.\x*, ilizwe eligeleza uchago loluju\x + Eks. 3.8.\x*.
\s Izibusiso zelizwe elithenjisiweyo
\p
\v 10 Ngoba ilizwe ongena kilo ukudla ilifa lalo kalinjengelizwe leGibhithe eliphuma kilo, lapho owahlanyela khona inhlanyelo yakho, wayithelela ngonyawo lwakho, njengesivande semibhida\x + Zek. 14.18.\x*;
\v 11 kodwa ilizwe elichaphela kilo ukudla ilifa lalo liyilizwe lamaqaqa lezigodi, linatha amanzi ngezulu lamazulu\x + 8.7.\x*;
\v 12 ilizwe iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho elikhathalelayo; amehlo eN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho aphezu kwalo njalo, kusukela ekuqaleni komnyaka kuze kube sekupheleni komnyaka\x + 1 Kho. 9.3.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Kuzakuthi-ke, uba lilalela lokulalela imithetho yami engililaya yona lamuhla, ukuthanda iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu, lokuyikhonza ngenhliziyo yenu yonke langomphefumulo wenu wonke\x + 6.5.\x*,
\v 14 ngizanika izulu lelizwe lenu ngesikhathi salo\x + Levi 26.4. Dute. 28.12.\x*, izulu elokuqala lezulu lokucina, ukuze ubuthe amabele akho lewayini lakho elitsha lamafutha akho\x + Jer. 5.24. Hos. 6.3. Jow. 2.23. Jak. 5.7.\x*.
\v 15 Ngizanika izifuyo zakho utshani edlelweni lakho\x + Hlab. 104.14.\x*, njalo uzakudla, usuthe\x + 6.11. Jow. 2.19.\x*.
\v 16 Ziqapheleni, hlezi inhliziyo yenu ikhohliseke, liphambuke\x + Jobe 31.27. Dute. 29.18.\x*, likhonze abanye onkulunkulu, libakhothamele\x + 8.19; 30.17.\x*,
\v 17 ukuze ulaka lweN\nd kosi\nd* lulivuthele\x + 6.15.\x*, njalo ivale amazulu, ukuze kungabi khona izulu\x + 1 Kho. 8.35. 2 Lan. 6.26. 7.13.\x*, lelizwe lingatheli isivuno salo\x + Levi 26. 4.\x*, libhubhe masinyane lisuke elizweni elihle iN\nd kosi\nd* elinika lona\x + 4.26. 30.18. Josh. 23.13,15,16.\x*.
\p
\v 18 Ngakho lizabeka lamazwi ami enhliziyweni yenu lemphefumulweni wenu\x + 6.6.\x*, liwabophele esandleni senu abe luphawu, ukuze abe \w ngamafilakteriyu\w** phakathi laphakathi kwamehlo enu\x + 6.8. Eks. 13.9.\x*.
\v 19 Lizawafundisa abantwana benu, ukhulume ngawo lapho uhlezi endlini yakho, lalapho uhamba endleleni, lalapho ulala, lalapho uvuka\x + 4.9.\x*.
\v 20 Liwabhale emigubazini yendlu yakho lemasangweni akho\x + 6.9.\x*,
\v 21 ukuze zande insuku zenu lensuku zabantwana benu, elizweni iN\nd kosi\nd* eyalifungela oyihlo ukubanika lona\x + Zaga 4.10. 9.11. Dute. 4.40. 6.2. Zaga 3.2.\x*, njengensuku zamazulu phezu komhlaba\x + Hlab. 89.29.\x*.
\p
\v 22 Ngoba uba ligcina lokugcina yonke imithetho le engililaya ukuthi liyenze, ukuthanda iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu, ukuhamba ngendlela zayo zonke\x + 6.17.\x*, lokunamathela kuyo\x + 10.20.\x*,
\v 23 khona iN\nd kosi\nd* izaxotsha elifeni zonke lezizizwe zisuke phambi kwenu\x + 4.38.\x*, lidle ilifa lezizwe ezinkulu lezilamandla kulani\x + 9.1.\x*.
\v 24 Yonke indawo lapho ingaphansi yonyawo lwenu ezanyathela khona izakuba ngeyenu\x + Josh. 1.3. Josh. 14.9.\x*; kusukela enkangala, leLebhanoni, kusukela emfuleni, umfula iYufrathi\x + Gen. 15.18. Eks. 23.31. Nani 34.3-12. Dute. 1.7. Josh. 1.4.\x*, kuze kufike elwandle lokucina, kuzakuba ngumngcele wenu\x + 34.2. Josh. 15.12.\x*.
\v 25 Kakulamuntu ozakuma phambi kwenu\x + 7.24.\x*; iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu izabeka ukwesabeka kwenu lokutshaywa luvalo ngani phezu kwalo lonke ilizwe elizanyathela kulo\x + 2.25.\x*, njengalokhu etshilo kini\x + Eks. 23.27.\x*.
\p
\v 26 Khangelani, lamuhla ngiyabeka phambi kwenu isibusiso lesiqalekiso\x + 30.1,15,19.\x*;
\v 27 isibusiso, uba lilalela imithetho yeN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu engililaya yona lamuhla\x + 28.2-14.\x*;
\v 28 lesiqalekiso, uba lingalaleli imithetho yeN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu, kodwa liphambuka endleleni engililaya yona lamuhla\x + 28.15-45.\x*, ukulandela abanye onkulunkulu elingabazanga\x + 6.14.\x*.
\v 29 Kuzakuthi lapho iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho esekungenisile elizweni oya kulo ukudla ilifa lalo, uzabeka isibusiso phezu kwentaba yeGerizimi, lesiqalekiso phezu kwentaba yeEbhali\x + 27.12,13. Josh. 8.33.\x*.
\v 30 Angithi zona ziphetsheya kweJordani emva kwendlela yekutshoneni kwelanga, elizweni lamaKhanani ahlala emagcekeni maqondana leGiligali, eduze lezihlahla \w zama-okhi\w**\x + Gen. 13.18.\x* zeMore\x + Gen. 12.6. Hlu. 7.1.\x*?
\v 31 Ngoba lizachapha iJordani ukuze lingene lidle ilifa lelizwe iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu elinika lona. Lizakudla ilifa lalo, lihlale kilo\x + 9.1.\x*,
\v 32 linanzelele ukwenza zonke izimiso lezahlulelo engizibeka phambi kwenu lamuhla\x + 5.32. 12.32.\x*.